MESSAGE.value: First commit of the Java version of cov-analyse-metrics. This implementation only focuses on reading configuration for analysis from both a JSON configuration file and command line options.

Adding support for: - Generation of the JSON file for cov-import-results - Exclusion of source file by regular expressions - Multiple thresholds per checkers - Comments in the JSON Configuration file - many more ...
